Detailed Description

This InputMapper supports the following methods:
  • Traditional Chinese Stroke
    • Simplified Chinese Stoke
    • Pinyin (Traditional Chinese Phonetic)
    • Bopofomo (Simplified Chinese Phonetic) (and English from the base class)
